| Illustrated cards | `exercises[type=illustrated_cards].cards[]` вҖ” **`label` only**; set `ttsIncludeSublabels: true` to join sublabels into one clip | Female (Achernar) | **Pro** (`Read aloud in a warm, welcoming tone.`) вҖ” better intonation on short phrases than Flash |
| Image labeling | `words/{image.id}.mp3` for images **not** covered by an illustrated card with the same `id` (e.g. a flag-only country) | Female | Flash |
| Dialogues | `exercises[type=dialogues].sections[].lines[]` | Per speaker | Pro |
