| Grammar examples | `exercises[type=grammar_examples].examples[]` | Female by default; set `voiceGender: 'male'` on a card for Charon | Pro (Flash only if `ttsFlash`); **exception:** IDs in `GRAMMAR_PRO_ACHERNAR_ONLY_IDS` вҶ’ **Pro + Achernar for every card** |
| Grammar highlight (`interactiveExamples`) | `grammarHighlight.exampleTtsTexts[]` / `examples[]` | Female | Flash by default; **Pro + Achernar** for IDs in `GRAMMAR_PRO_ACHERNAR_ONLY_IDS` |
