| Reading text images (flip cards) | `exercises[type=reading_text].images[]` when `ttsWordId` + `label` СҒР° Р·Р°РҙР°РҙРөРҪРё вҶ’ `words/{ttsWordId}.mp3` | Female | Flash (Pro Р°РәРҫ `ttsWordId` Рө РІ `READING_TEXT_IMAGE_STRESS_IDS`) |
